[src:win-loss-record-pitching/2021-major-league-baseball-all-star-game] **^** Manny Machado was named as the roster replacement for Ronald Acuña Jr. due to injury.
[src:win-loss-record-pitching/2021-major-league-baseball-all-star-game] **^** Cedric Mullins was named starter in place of Mike Trout due to injury.
[src:win-loss-record-pitching/2021-major-league-baseball-all-star-game] **^** Bryan Reynolds was named starter in place of Ronald Acuña Jr. due to injury.
